name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.qjournal.queued-edits.limit.mb
description: Queue size in MB for quorum journal edits.

name: dfs.balancer.max-no-move-interval
description:
If this specified amount of time has elapsed and no block has been moved
    out of a source DataNode, on more effort will be made to move blocks out of
    this DataNode in the current Balancer iteration.

name: tfile.fs.output.buffer.size
description: Buffer size used for FSDataOutputStream in bytes.

name: mapreduce.job.encrypted-intermediate-data-key-size-bits
description: Mapreduce encrypt data key size default is 128

name: ha.failover-controller.cli-check.rpc-timeout.ms
description: Timeout that the CLI (manual) FC waits for monitorHealth, getServiceState

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.client.job.max-retries
description:
The number of retries the client will make for getJob and
    dependent calls.
    This is needed for non-HDFS DFS where additional, high level
    retries are required to avoid spurious failures during the getJob call.
    30 is a good value for WASB

name: dfs.namenode.blockreport.max.lock.hold.time
description: The BlockReportProcessingThread max write lock hold time in ms.

name: hadoop.security.kms.client.timeout
description:
Sets value for KMS client connection timeout, and the read timeout
    to KMS servers.
